        p.lead.text-center Simply-priced plans for businesses and enterprises.
        a.btn.orange-bg.border-none.white.arrow(href="/dashboard/signup" style="font-size:1.2em; padding:1rem 2.7rem 1rem; margin:30px 0 50px;") Get started, free
    
    .row.margin-top-less.pricing
        .column.large-6.fade-in-right.delay-2.min-padding
          .pricing-table.radius.bg-white.margin-bottom
            .row.blue-pale-bg.padding-vertical
              h2.white.text-center.light.letter-spacing-1.uppercase  Starter
            .row
              .column.large-12.text-center.border-bottom-gray
                  .top-panel.margin-vertical
                    h2.text-center.blue-medium(style="font-size:3em;") Free
                    div
                      b 30 Transactions / Month
                      br
                      b Up to $1,000 Daily
                      br
                      small 1% applied to additional transactions
            .row.text-center
              .column.large-12.margin-vertical
                ul.list-style-none.margin-none
                  li.bold Core Features
                  li Payment & Refund Managment
                  li Payment Tools
                  li Shopping Cart Plugins
                  li API, Libraries, & SDKs
                  li CSV Ledger Download
                  li Hosted Solutions
                  br
                  li.bold Settlement
                  li Weekly USD/EUR Settlements
                  small (ACH to USA & SEPA to Euro)
                  li Daily Bitcoin Settlements
                  small (All Supported Countries)
                  br
                  li.bold Support
                  li Email Support
                    
        .column.large-6.fade-in-right.delay-3.min-padding
          .pricing-table.radius.bg-white.margin-bottom
            .row(style="background-color:#204096; padding:40px 0 25px;")
              h2.white.text-center.light.uppercase.letter-spacing-1 Business
            .row
              .column.large-12.text-center.border-bottom-gray
                  .top-panel.margin-vertical
                    h2.blue-medium(style="font-size:4em; line-height: 0.8;") 1%
                    small.text-center(style="display:block;") Transaction Fee
                    div
                    br  
                    b Unlimited Transactions
                    br
                    br

            .row.text-center
              .column.large-12.margin-vertical
                ul.list-style-none.margin-none.padding-horizontal
                  .bold * All the Core Features of <br />the Starter Plan Plus:
                  br 
                  li Multi-User Login Access
                  li Priority Email Support
                  li Demandware Cartridge
                  li Quickbooks IIF Download
                  br
                  li.bold Settlement
                  li Daily Bitcoin Settlements
                  small (All Supported Countries)
                  li Daily Bank Settlements
                  small (EFT to Canada, SPEI to Mexico,<br /> ACH to USA, SEPA to Euro)
                  li Bank Transfers to:
                  small (UK, BRA, ZAF, AUS, NZL)
        
      .text-center
        .enterprise-card.bg-blue.white.radius.fade-in-right.delay-4
          .row
              h4.uppercase.margin-vertical-less Enterprise Plan
              ul.remove-bullets.margin-bottom-none
                li Dedicated Account Manager
                li Bank transfers to all permissible countries
                li Masspay & Payroll solutions
                li Additional platform customization
              .margin-top-less.margin-bottom
                a(href="mailto:sales@bitpay.com").arrow.white.btn.btn-blue-border.uppercase.bold.margin-left-less.btn-margin Contact Us
                br
                a(href="/enterprise").white Learn More

  .section
    .row
      .column.medium-10.medium-offset-1.large-5.large-offset-1
        .margin-bottom
          h5 Guaranteed Instant Conversion Rate
          p Buyers will always get a better value by spending their bitcoins at a BitPay merchant than by selling them on an exchange. We pool the order books of active bitcoin exchanges, and find the best bid worldwide. We call this the Bitcoin Best Bid (BBB) rate. BitPay guarantees the bitcoin-to-fiat <a href="https://bitpay.com/bitcoin-exchange-rates">exchange rate</a> at the point of sale, so our merchants are protected from bitcoin price fluctuations.
        div
          h5 Get Paid In Bitcoin
          p Many of our merchants choose to take a percentage of their BitPay settlement in bitcoin, or even 100%. You can choose your settlement preferences from your account dashboard. We settle bitcoin to your bitcoin address daily.
          
      .column.medium-10.medium-offset-1.large-5.large-offset-0.end
        .margin-bottom
          h5 Simple Pricing for all Plans
          p Our Starter plan offers free, instant conversions for up to 30 transactions a month, weekly settlements in two currencies, and daily settlements  in bitcoin. The Business Plan offers daily settlements in nine currencies and unlimited monthly transactions for a 1% settlement fee.
        div
          h5 Can you process payments for regulated industries?
          p We are able to process payments for most businesses, but sometimes legal and regulatory concerns prevent us from servicing #[a(href="/about/terms#prohibited") some industries]. We'd like to provide all legal businesses the opportunity to accept bitcoin, and we are constantly working to make that a possibility.
      .column.medium-10.medium-offset-1.large-5.large-offset-1
      .column.medium-10.medium-offset-1.large-5.large-offset-0.end

  .section.bg-lightblue-gradient.border-top-gray
    .row
      .column.large-10.large-offset-1.text-center
          h3.white Get access to the BitPay platform.
          .margin-top-less
            a(href="/dashboard/signup").white.btn.btn-blue-solid.uppercase.bold.btn-margin.arrow Accept Bitcoin
